title: Expect domestic two-wheeler sales to reach peak levels of FY19 latest by Q1 FY26: Bajaj Auto
description: In FY24, domestic two-wheeler sales were at 1.8 crore units, according to Society of Indian Automobile Manufacturers data. One of the key factors driving growth of two-wheeler sales is the bounce back of retail financing, he said.
